  "body": "### What's your issue about?\r\nThere seems to be a strange scenario where parsing a zero byte string cause convert to fail.\r\n\r\n```python\r\n@public\r\ndef zero_bytes(inp: bytes <= 1) -> int128:\r\n    return convert(inp, 'int128')\r\n```\r\nTest case\r\n```python\r\n    assert c.zero_bytes(b'\\x01') == 1\r\n    assert c.zero_bytes(b'\\x00') == 0\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/ethereum/vyper/pull/696 for more details.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\n\r\nBusy investigating\r\n\r\n#### Cute Animal Picture\r\n![](https://img.purch.com/w/660/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5saXZlc2NpZW5jZS5jb20vaW1hZ2VzL2kvMDAwLzAyNC8xODgvb3JpZ2luYWwvc2xlZXBpbmcta2l0dGVuLmpwZw==)\r\n",
